idam eva vyanakti. īṣanmukulitapakṣmayugalā nāsāgraviniveśitā yugamātravyavalokinī vā kāryā dṛṣṭiḥ.

<commentary>prathamārambhiṇaḥ saṃtatābhyāsena kleśasya parihārārtham āha.

dṛṣṭicittaparikhedaparityāgāya kadācit karhicit diśo vyavalokayet. atha kadācit kaścit tatsamīpam āgacchet, tadā tasya praticchāyāmātraṃ viditvā svāgatavādena saṃtoṣaṇārthaṃ vilokayet. anyathā tatra tasyāvadhyānenākuśalaṃ prasavet.</commentary>

mārge 'pi tathādṛṣṭer gacchata upaghātaparihārārtham āha. bhayahetucaurādipratipattyarthaṃ caturdiśam iti krameṇa. anyathātmabhāvasya rakṣā kṛtā na syāt.